      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, those are good foundational points. can you expand on the economic argument specifically? my students often struggle to articulate the connection between stricter enforcement and the domestic labor market without sounding like they're just being dismissive of migrant workers. how would a sophisticated debater frame the economic benefits of stricter controls in a way that focuses on wage stability and public resource management?",
